        "description": "# Threadly.com\n\n**Threadly** is a modern real-time chat platform that brings people closer together through instant messaging, video calls, and file sharing.\n\nKey features of Threadly include:\n\n1. **üí¨ Real-time Chat:** Enjoy instant messaging with individuals or groups.\n2. **üé• Live Video:** Connect face-to-face with high-quality live video calls.\n\n3. **üìé Send Attachments:** Easily share photos, videos, documents, and other files.\n\n4. **üë• Group Conversations:** Create and manage group chats with friends, family, or teams.\n\n5. **‚ú® Modern UX:** A sleek, responsive interface designed for speed and simplicity.\n\n6. **üîí Secure Communication:** Protect your messages with secure data handling.\n\nThreadly focuses on providing a fast, engaging, and feature-rich communication experience for everyone.\n\n## üèÅ Installation\n\nClone the repository and follow the [README](https://github.com/Barmanji/chatOliver_monorepo) to install dependencies and configure environment variables.\n\n## üêû Reporting issues\n\nIf you find bugs or issues, please open an issue on the project's [GitHub repository.](https://github.com/Barmanji/chatOliver_monorepo/issues/new)",
